data.description: A dream kitchen and close to a menu of dining and shopping options! Gutted and rebuilt from the ground up. This delightful 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom house begins to impress as you cross the threshold. Beautiful bamboo flooring is located throughout the entryway, living areas, and kitchen. The attractive U-shaped chef's kitchen is gorgeous with fresh updates including customer cabinetry, a pantry and granite countertops with ample counter space for food prep. All major appliances stay for your convenience. The main-floor primary bedroom cannot be beat with a walk-in closet. The full unfinished basement is a goldmine of potential, whether you have in mind a rec room, guest room, studio, or a secluded home office. Attractive landscaping maximizes the value of the large .39-acre yard with a custom fire pit. The recently updated backyard deck is crafted of pressure-treated wood and is great for relaxing or grilling your favorite foods. Facing the tranquil, low-traffic street, a front breezy porch is a nice spot for enjoying refreshments, whether morning coffee or twilight nightcap. This home includes a one car detached garage and easy access to an array of local amenities, various shopping/dining/entertainment destinations (5 mins from Greene Shopping Center and 14 mins from Fraze Pavillion) and Wright Patterson Air Force Base. Your future self will thank you for acting fast on this one!
